.06017]},{"section":7,"text":"Then there's oral lichen planus, which also causes redness but usually comes with other symptoms like white patches or a lacy pattern.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038324,0.050445,0.062603,0.076577,0.089632,0.101,0.11022,0.11198,0.11555,0.11882,0.085245,0.039591],"unified_progress":[0.040965,0.064934,0.086133,0.093884,0.099226,0.10779,0.10318,0.10018,0.094351,0.087238,0.069757,0.052368]},{"section":8,"text":"And then there's oral thrush, which would probably have white patches that you can scrape off, kind of like cottage cheese.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030194,0.046388,0.060971,0.07648,0.090427,0.1027,0.11216,0.11554,0.11923,0.11975,0.085567,0.040605],"unified_progress":[0.036243,0.063321,0.082711,0.093552,0.099718,0.10602,0.10358,0.1015,0.096826,0.090834,0.071941,0.053751]},{"section":9,"text":"But wait, none of those really match exactly what the foster mom saw.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031344,0.045766,0.057663,0.068291,0.078561,0.091074,0.10279,0.1146,0.12362,0.12289,0.10138,0.062037],"unified_progress":[0.039323,0.061773,0.073645,0.081691,0.090913,0.093678,0.096561,0.10118,0.10022,0.1047,0.088515,0.067796]},{"section":10,"text":"So let's focus on geographic tongue.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.013596,0.049891,0.07783,0.09431,0.10159,0.10629,0.10632,0.10875,0.10856,0.10786,0.081977,0.043031],"unified_progress":[0.032061,0.066297,0.079102,0.093464,0.0944,0.094045,0.10419,0.095837,0.093346,0.10019,0.083758,0.063321]},{"section":11,"text":"It's known for having these red patches that change shape and location.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.0402,0.049597,0.059406,0.070262,0.080751,0.089744,0.098803,0.10204,0.10809,0.11637,0.10844,0.076297],"unified_progress":[0.044392,0.061449,0.07359,0.082106,0.090576,0.099276,0.09764,0.099131,0.096921,0.095198,0.085886,0.073835]},{"section":12,"text":"They don't stay put; they wander around.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.10999,0.089009,0.082222,0.07339,0.074443,0.07717,0.080173,0.089718,0.081378,0.056992,0.061148,0.12437],"unified_progress":[0.2039,0.078754,0.062989,0.063742,0.073015,0.073246,0.09536,0.081887,0.079217,0.064669,0.06063,0.062591]},{"section":13,"text":"The fact that the redness appeared only when brushing teeth makes me think it might be more noticeable under stress or irritation.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.069058,0.068084,0.075393,0.081879,0.084919,0.086992,0.088875,0.08786,0.088964,0.094604,0.095786,0.077586],"unified_progress":[0.073322,0.087071,0.061245,0.087829,0.090184,0.097182,0.09361,0.089677,0.087211,0.084406,0.079077,0.069185]},{"section":14,"text":"Hmm, that sounds like what's happening here.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.1209,0.098398,0.088731,0.076839,0.076042,0.076711,0.077872,0.085631,0.077117,0.053305,0.05632,0.11213],"unified_progress":[0.22114,0.087682,0.06226,0.063099,0.073454,0.072236,0.088483,0.078341,0.075393,0.061842,0.057524,0.058552]},{"section":15,"text":"But hold on, let's consider if there's anything else it could be.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019038,0.052088,0.075978,0.086598,0.092744,0.09941,0.10685,0.11585,0.11907,0.11533,0.081183,0.035872],"unified_progress":[0.038167,0.080214,0.067877,0.090699,0.10164,0.096281,0.095716,0.10316,0.099027,0.094334,0.079906,0.052977]},{"section":16,"text":"Oral lichen planus does have red areas too, but it often has other features like a lacy pattern or bumps.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027262,0.039999,0.054643,0.069226,0.082743,0.096209,0.1089,0.11649,0.12317,0.12713,0.10088,0.05334],"unified_progress":[0.03753,0.05917,0.075625,0.08623,0.095455,0.10402,0.10193,0.10358,0.10063,0.097098,0.080461,0.05